FORMAT: 1A

# 网络设备管理API

网络设备管理系统API文档，支持交换机、路由器等网络设备的配置和监控。

HOST: http://network-manager:8080

## 设备信息 [/api/devices]

### 获取设备列表 [GET /api/devices{?type,status}]

获取所有网络设备的列表信息

+ Parameters
    + type: `switch` (string, optional) - 设备类型（switch, router, firewall）
    + status: `online` (string, optional) - 设备状态（online, offline, unknown）

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body

            {
                "status": "success",
                "data": {
                    "devices": [
                        {
                            "device_id": "sw-001",
                            "name": "Core Switch 1",
                            "type": "switch",
                            "ip_address": "192.168.1.10",
                            "status": "online",
                            "uptime": 86400,
                            "last_seen": "2024-01-15T11:00:00Z"
                        }
                    ],
                    "total": 1
                }
            }

### 添加新设备 [POST /api/devices]

向系统中添加新的网络设备

+ Request (application/json)
    + Body

            {
                "name": "Access Switch 1",
                "type": "switch",
                "ip_address": "192.168.1.20",
                "snmp_community": "public",
                "location": "Building A Floor 1"
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Body

            {
                "status": "success",
                "message": "Device added successfully",
                "data": {
                    "device_id": "sw-002",
                    "name": "Access Switch 1",
                    "status": "pending"
                }
            }

## 设备配置 [/api/devices/{device_id}]

### 获取设备详情 [GET /api/devices/{device_id}]

获取指定设备的详细信息和配置

+ Parameters
    + device_id: `sw-001` (string, required) - 设备ID

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body

            {
                "status": "success",
                "data": {
                    "device_id": "sw-001",
                    "name": "Core Switch 1",
                    "type": "switch",
                    "ip_address": "192.168.1.10",
                    "status": "online",
                    "ports": [
                        {
                            "port_id": "1/0/1",
                            "name": "GigabitEthernet1/0/1",
                            "status": "up",
                            "speed": "1000Mbps",
                            "duplex": "full"
                        }
                    ],
                    "vlans": [
                        {
                            "vlan_id": 100,
                            "name": "Management",
                            "status": "active"
                        }
                    ]
                }
            }

### 更新设备配置 [PUT /api/devices/{device_id}/config]

更新设备的配置信息

+ Parameters
    + device_id: `sw-001` (string, required) - 设备ID

+ Request (application/json)
    + Body

            {
                "vlans": [
                    {
                        "vlan_id": 200,
                        "name": "Production",
                        "action": "add"
                    }
                ],
                "ports": [
                    {
                        "port_id": "1/0/2",
                        "vlan": 200,
                        "mode": "access"
                    }
                ]
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body

            {
                "status": "success",
                "message": "Configuration updated successfully",
                "data": {
                    "changes_applied": 2,
                    "rollback_id": "rb-001"
                }
            }

## 端口管理 [/api/devices/{device_id}/ports]

### 获取端口状态 [GET /api/devices/{device_id}/ports]

获取设备所有端口的状态信息

+ Parameters
    + device_id: `sw-001` (string, required) - 设备ID

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body

            {
                "status": "success",
                "data": {
                    "ports": [
                        {
                            "port_id": "1/0/1",
                            "name": "GigabitEthernet1/0/1",
                            "status": "up",
                            "admin_status": "up",
                            "speed": "1000Mbps",
                            "duplex": "full",
                            "vlan": 100,
                            "mode": "access",
                            "traffic": {
                                "rx_bytes": 1024000,
                                "tx_bytes": 2048000,
                                "rx_packets": 1000,
                                "tx_packets": 2000,
                                "errors": 0
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                }
            }

### 配置端口 [PUT /api/devices/{device_id}/ports/{port_id}]

配置指定端口的参数

+ Parameters
    + device_id: `sw-001` (string, required) - 设备ID
    + port_id: `1/0/1` (string, required) - 端口ID

+ Request (application/json)
    + Body

            {
                "admin_status": "up",
                "vlan": 200,
                "mode": "access",
                "description": "Server Connection"
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body

            {
                "status": "success",
                "message": "Port configuration updated",
                "data": {
                    "port_id": "1/0/1",
                    "previous_config": {
                        "vlan": 100,
                        "mode": "access"
                    },
                    "new_config": {
                        "vlan": 200,
                        "mode": "access"
                    }
                }
            }

## 网络监控 [/api/monitoring]

### 获取网络流量统计 [GET /api/monitoring/traffic{?device_id,time_range}]

获取网络设备的流量统计信息

+ Parameters
    + device_id: `sw-001` (string, optional) - 指定设备ID，不指定则返回所有设备
    + time_range: `1h` (string, optional) - 时间范围（1h, 6h, 24h, 7d）

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Body

            {
                "status": "success",
                "data": {
                    "time_range": "1h",
                    "devices": [
                        {
                            "device_id": "sw-001",
                            "total_rx_bytes": 10240000,
                            "total_tx_bytes": 20480000,
                            "peak_utilization": 45.2,
                            "average_utilization": 32.1,
                            "ports": [
                                {
                                    "port_id": "1/0/1",
                                    "rx_bytes": 5120000,
                                    "tx_bytes": 10240000,
                                    "utilization": 40.5
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                }
            }

### 设置监控告警 [POST /api/monitoring/alerts]

创建新的监控告警规则

+ Request (application/json)
    + Body

            {
                "name": "High CPU Alert",
                "device_id": "sw-001",
                "metric": "cpu_usage",
                "threshold": 80,
                "operator": "greater_than",
                "duration": 300,
                "notification": {
                    "email": ["admin@company.com"],
                    "webhook": "http://alerting-system:8080/webhook"
                }
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)
    + Body

            {
                "status": "success",
                "message": "Alert rule created successfully",
                "data": {
                    "alert_id": "alert-001",
                    "status": "active"
                }
            }